snippet.title: ANGRY KING Gameplay 👑 Pranks 1 to 5 😜 Keplerians NEW GAME
snippet.description:
Our brand new game ANGRY KING 👑 has finally released! And today we will upload the first 5 pranks of the game... We hope you're having a great time playing Angry King! We put a lot of effort to bring an amazing game to our community. Leave your comments below! 👇

ANGRY KING 👑
🔸 G-Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.keplerians.angryking
🔹 App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/angry-king-scary-game/id6446140549

Want to see a behind the scenes of how the music of Angry King was made? Check it out! 🎶 https://youtu.be/MOQBIOLiboU
